2 Hz PerfPro export of Moxy data

Source: R/data.R
moxy_ramp.xlsx.Rd

Exported from PerfPro Studio software, recorded at 0.5 Hz no smoothing and exported at 2 Hz. Containing a ramp incremental cycling protocol, placed on bilateral vastus lateralis muscle sites. With data errors (outliers, invalid data, missing NA values) introduced to demonstrate mnirs package functionality.

Format

.xlsx file with six columns and 2203 rows.

  • nirs_channels = c("SmO2 Live", "SmO2 Live(2)")

  • time_channel = c("hh:mm:ss)

  • event_channel = c("Lap)

Developed by Jem Arnold.

Site built with pkgdown 2.2.0.
